---
title: Pork Schnitzel & Roast Capsicum Veggie Toss with Peri-Peri Sauce
description: We’re putting a pep in this pork schnitzel’s step by drizzling it in a peri peri-honey sauce. It will cut through the
crunch, and sitting it on top of a roast veggie toss will really make this dish fun. You’ll be skipping to the dinner table
in anticipation.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65dff7abf67b1654d361e06c-8835e28f.jpeg
